doc.body:
This hook is [SWR powered](https://docs.reservoir.tools/docs/hooks#swr-powered-hooks) and also handles [infinite loading UX](https://docs.reservoir.tools/docs/hooks#infinite-loading-hooks). The hook is an extension of the [useListings](doc:uselistings) hook. It's a convenient way to fetch the listings that belong to the currently connected wallet. The parameters are exactly the same as the aforementioned useListings hook.
[block:code]
{
  "codes": [
    {
      "code": "import { useOwnerListings } from '@reservoir0x/reservoir-kit-ui'\n\n const {\n   data: listings,\n   fetchNextPage,\n   hasNextPage,\n } = useOwnerListings()",
      "language": "typescript"
    }
  ]
}
[/block]
